PN,41101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784900897
OL,3,C'Extremely significant' bomb found as
OL,4,Ccar intercepted near NI border
OL,6,FAn "extremely significant" bomb has
OL,7,Fbeen discovered after a car was
OL,8,Fintercepted near the Northern Ireland
OL,9,Fborder in an operation targeting
OL,10,Fdissident republicans, the Republic of
OL,11,FIreland's police force An Garda
OL,12,FSiochana have said.
OL,14,FIt is understood the bomb was being
OL,15,Fdriven across the border for an attack
OL,16,Fin Northern Ireland.
OL,26,@nD@DOUnD@ZO]tD@BrttD@Frp
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784900897
OL,3,C'Extremely significant' bomb found as
OL,4,Ccar intercepted near NI border
OL,6,FMembers of the Garda's Special
OL,7,FDetective Unit stopped the vehicle in
OL,8,Fan intelligence-led operation,
OL,9,Ftravelling on the N2 south of
OL,10,FCarrickmacross, Co Monaghan on
OL,11,FWednesday afternoon.
OL,13,FGardai then requested the assistance
OL,14,Fof the Irish Defence Forces EOD
OL,15,F(Explosive Ordnance Disposal) team,
OL,16,Fwhich completed an examination of the
OL,17,Fvehicle.
OL,19,FThe female driver, aged in her 20s,
OL,20,Fwas arrested at the scene and remained
OL,21,Fin Garda custody on Friday.
OL,26,@uD@Frt
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784900897
OL,3,C'Extremely significant' bomb found as
OL,4,Ccar intercepted near NI border
OL,6,FAnother suspect, a man aged in his
OL,7,F40s, has since been arrested and is
OL,8,Fbeing held at a Garda station in the
OL,9,FDublin area.
OL,11,F'Explosive device'
OL,13,FGarda Commissioner Justin Kelly
OL,14,Fconfirmed details of the operation as
OL,15,Fhe spoke at a Garda graduation event
OL,16,Fin Co Tipperary on Friday.
OL,18,F"To be clear, what we found was an
OL,19,Fextremely significant seizure," he
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,26,@zD@AOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784900897
OL,3,C'Extremely significant' bomb found as
OL,4,Ccar intercepted near NI border
OL,6,F"So this was an explosive device."
OL,8,FCommissioner Kelly added: "Any seizure
OL,9,Fof this nature is really concerning.
OL,11,F"However, we certainly know that there
OL,12,Fare a small minority of dissident
OL,13,Frepublicans who did not agree with the
OL,14,FGood Friday Agreement, they did not
OL,15,Fput weapons and explosives (out of
OL,16,Fuse), they didn't, you know, go
OL,17,Fthrough with the proper process in
OL,18,Frelation to decommissioning.
OL,20,F"So that is something that we continue
OL,21,Fto deal with.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@bO]pD@[OUsD@AOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784900897
OL,3,C'Extremely significant' bomb found as
OL,4,Ccar intercepted near NI border
OL,6,F"There's a small minority of these
OL,7,Findividuals, I would describe them as
OL,8,Fradicalised republicans, and this is a
OL,9,Fthreat that we're going to continue to
OL,10,Fface for some time."
OL,12,FMr Kelly indicated that the bomb was
OL,13,Falready constructed when it was seized.
OL,15,F"Unfortunately for operational
OL,16,Freasons, I can't go into the exact
OL,17,Fdetail of the device," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOUyD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784900897
OL,3,C'Extremely significant' bomb found as
OL,4,Ccar intercepted near NI border
OL,6,F"But what I will say certainly it was
OL,7,Fa significant explosive device. So
OL,8,Fcertainly not just the seizure of
OL,9,Fcomponents or pieces.
OL,11,F"This was an explosive device and it
OL,12,Fwould have or could have potentially
OL,13,Fcaused significant damage."
OL,15,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland
OL,16,F(PSNI) Assistant Chief Constable Davy
OL,17,FBeck said police on both sides of the
OL,18,FIrish border shared a "joint
OL,19,Fcommitment" to tackle the dissident
OL,20,Frepublican terror threat.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@[O]zD@WOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784900897
OL,3,C'Extremely significant' bomb found as
OL,4,Ccar intercepted near NI border
OL,6,F"I very much welcome this significant
OL,7,Fseizure and the arrests made by our
OL,8,Fcolleagues in An Garda Siochana, with
OL,9,Fwhom we work very closely on a daily
OL,10,Fbasis," he said.
OL,12,F"This underlines our joint commitment
OL,13,Fto address the threat posed by violent
OL,14,Fdissident republican groups and keep
OL,15,Fcommunities safe.
OL,17,F"We will continue to liaise closely
OL,18,Fwith An Garda Siochana in relation to
OL,19,Ftheir investigation, and provide any
OL,20,Fsupport as required."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@YrtpD@]rprD@GO]tD@AOUyD@AOUzD@
OL,26,APrtzD@Trp|D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784900897
OL,3,C'Extremely significant' bomb found as
OL,4,Ccar intercepted near NI border
OL,6,F'Deeply concerning'
OL,8,FSecretary of State for Northern
OL,9,FIreland Sir Chris Bryant commended the
OL,10,FGarda for intercepting the device.
OL,12,F"Huge thanks to An Garda Siochana for
OL,13,Ftheir quick, decisive action in Co.
OL,14,FMonaghan," he posted on social media.
OL,16,F"Intercepting a dangerous device like
OL,17,Fthis undoubtedly saved lives and kept
OL,18,Fcommunities safe on both sides of the
OL,19,Fborder.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@[rttD@_rpvD@JO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784900897
OL,3,C'Extremely significant' bomb found as
OL,4,Ccar intercepted near NI border
OL,6,F"Strong cross-border security
OL,7,Fcooperation remains as vital as ever."
OL,9,FOn social media, Northern Ireland's
OL,10,Fdeputy First Minister Emma Little-
OL,11,FPengelly MLA described the seizure as
OL,12,F"deeply concerning" and said she has
OL,13,Fasked for an "urgent briefing".
OL,15,FDUP Leader Gavin Robinson MP said the
OL,16,Fincident was "chilling" and "could
OL,17,Fhave resulted in the loss of life".
OL,19,FHe said those who stopped the bomb
OL,20,F"may have prevented innocent families
OL,21,Ffrom suffering unimaginable tragedy".
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784900897
OL,3,C'Extremely significant' bomb found as
OL,4,Ccar intercepted near NI border
OL,6,F"This operation also raises serious
OL,7,Fquestions for the Irish Government
OL,8,Fabout how it is assessing the threat
OL,9,Fposed by dissident republican
OL,10,Fterrorism and whether the response is
OL,11,Fkeeping pace with the danger," Mr
OL,12,FRobinson added.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784900897
OL,3,C'Extremely significant' bomb found as
OL,4,Ccar intercepted near NI border
OL,6,F"If terrorists are capable of
OL,7,Fassembling sophisticated explosive
OL,8,Fdevices and moving them towards the
OL,9,Fborder, then it is entirely legitimate
OL,10,Fto ask whether the threat is being
OL,11,Ffully recognised and whether
OL,12,Fsufficient resources and operational
OL,13,Ffocus are being directed towards
OL,14,Fdisrupting these organisations before
OL,15,Fthey reach this stage."
OL,17,F"This incident is a stark reminder
OL,18,Fthat these terrorists remain active,
OL,19,Forganised and intent on murder. There
OL,20,Fcan be no room for complacency.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784900897
OL,3,C'Extremely significant' bomb found as
OL,4,Ccar intercepted near NI border
OL,6,F"The response from both governments
OL,7,Fmust be relentless, intelligence-led
OL,8,Fand uncompromising."
OL,10,FSpeaking in Co Tipperary, Ireland's
OL,11,FMinister for Justice Jim O'Callaghan
OL,12,Fsaid it was "very worrying".
